# AMR-GigaWord 200k

# ::id 0 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok united nations secretary general kofi annan , slain u.n. envoy to iraq sergio vieira de mello and former chief weapons inspector hans blix made the shortlist for europe 's top human rights prize , the european parliament said wednesday .
# ::alignments
(s / say-01
      :ARG0 (g / government-organization
            :name (n / name
                  :op1 "Parliament")
            :mod (c / continent
                  :name (n2 / name
                        :op1 "Europe")))
      :ARG1 (m / make-18
            :ARG0 (a / and
                  :op1 (p / person
                        :name (n3 / name
                              :op1 "Kofi"
                              :op2 "Annan")
                        :ARG0-of (h / have-org-role-91
                              :ARG1 (o / organization
                                    :name (n4 / name
                                          :op1 "United"
                                          :op2 "Nations"))
                              :ARG2 (s2 / secretary
                                    :mod (g2 / general))))
                  :op2 (p2 / person
                        :name (n5 / name
                              :op1 "Sergio"
                              :op2 "Vieira"
                              :op3 "de"
                              :op4 "Mello")
                        :ARG1-of (s3 / slay-01)
                        :ARG0-of (h2 / have-org-role-91
                              :ARG1 (o2 / organization
                                    :name (n6 / name
                                          :op1 "United"
                                          :op2 "Nations"))
                              :ARG2 (e / envoy
                                    :mod (c2 / country
                                          :name (n7 / name
                                                :op1 "Iraq")))))
                  :op3 (p3 / person
                        :name (n8 / name
                              :op1 "Hans"
                              :op2 "Blix")
                        :ARG0-of (ii / inspect-01
                              :ARG1 (w / weapon)
                              :mod (c3 / chief)
                              :time (f / former))))
            :ARG1 (s4 / shortlist
                  :purpose (p4 / prize
                        :mod (r / right-05
                              :ARG1 (h3 / human))
                        :mod (t / top)
                        :poss o)))
      :time (w2 / wednesday))

# ::id 1 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok telecom italia mobile spa , an italian mobile phone operator , said monday that its turkish unit has filed a lawsuit seeking nearly $ us# billion in damages from turkey 's telecommunications industry regulator .
# ::alignments

      :ARG0 (c / company
            :name (n / name
                  :op1 "Telecom"
                  :op2 "Italian"
                  :op3 "Mobile"
                  :op4 "Spa")

                  :ARG1 (p / phone
                        :ARG1-of (m / mobile-02)))
            :mod (c2 / country
                  :name (n2 / name
                        :op1 "Italy")))
      :ARG1 (f / file-01
            :ARG0 (u / unit
                  :poss c
                  :mod c2
                  :name (n3 / name
                        :op1 "Turkey")))
      :ARG1 (s2 / sue-02
            :ARG0 u
            :ARG2 (d / damages-02
                  :ARG0 (p2 / person
                        :ARG0-of (r / regulate-01
                              :ARG1 (ii / industry
                                    :mod (t / telecommunication)
                                    :poss c2)))
                  :ARG1 (n4 / nearly
                        :op1 (m2 / monetary-quantity
                              :quant 1000000000
                              :unit (d2 / dollar)))))
      :time (d3 / date-entity
            :weekday (m3 / monday)))

# ::id 5 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred

            :ARG0 (s2 / strike-01
                  :path (a / air)
                  :mod (c / country
                        :name (n / name
                              :op1 "Israel"))
                  :location (s3 / south
                        :part-of (s4 / strip
                              :name (n2 / name
                                    :op1 "Gaza"))))
            :ARG1 (g2 / gunman
                  :quant 2
                  :mod (h / hamass))
            :time (o / operation
                  :mod (m2 / military)
                  :time (d / date-entity
                        :weekday (w / wednesday)))))

# ::id 6 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok at least ## countries -- as far away as colombia -- have banned chinese dairy imports in response to a widening tainted milk scandal that has claimed the lives of four chinese babies .
# ::alignments
(r / respond-01
      :ARG0 (c / country
            :quant (a / at-least)
            :ARG1-of (h / have-degree-91
                  :ARG2 (f / far)
                  :ARG3 (e / equal)
                  :ARG4 (c2 / country
                        :name (n / name
                              :op1 "Colombia"))))
      :ARG1 (s / scandal
            :topic (m / milk)
            :ARG1-of (t / taint-01)
            :ARG0-of (c3 / claim-02
                  :ARG1 (l / life
                        :poss (b / baby
                              :quant 4
                              :mod (c4 / country
                                    :name (n2 / name
                                          :op1 "China")))))
            :ARG1-of (w / widen-01))
      :ARG2 (b2 / ban-01
            :ARG0 c
            :ARG1 (ii / import-01
                  :ARG0 c4
                  :ARG1 m)))

(c / contrast-01
      :ARG1 (d / do-02
            :ARG1 (j / job
                  :quant "2/3"))
      :ARG2 (o / obligate-01
            :ARG2 (a / and
                  :op1 (r / reach-01
                        :ARG0 (c2 / charm
                              :mod (s / silver))
                        :ARG1 (d2 / down))
                  :op2 (p / perform-02
                        :ARG0 c2
                        :ARG1 (c3 / complete-01
                              :ARG0 c2
                              :ARG1 j
                              :manner (a2 / and
                                    :op1 (w / win-01
                                          :ARG0 c2
                                          :ARG1 (s2 / stake
                                                :mod (r2 / race-02)
                                                :quant (d3 / distance-quantity
                                                      :quant "1/2"
                                                      :unit (m / mile)))
                                          :duration (t / temporal-quantity
                                                :quant 3
                                                :unit (w2 / week)))
                                    :op2 (b / become-01
                                          :ARG1 c2
                                          :ARG2 (h / horse
                                                :ord (o2 / ordinal-entity
                                                      :value "-1")
                                                :ARG1-of (h2 / have-degree-91
                                                      :ARG2 (g / good-03
                                                            :ARG1 h)
                                                      :ARG3 (m2 / most)
                                                      :ARG5 (h3 / horse
                                                            :ARG0-of (s3 / sweep-02
                                                                  :ARG1 (c4 / crown
                                                                        :mod (t2 / triple))
                                                                  :time (h4 / history
                                                                        :mod r2))))))))))
            :time (n / now)))
